General.Name: Trajectory Alpha Acquisition Corp
General.Description: Zalatoris Acquisition Corp. does not have significant operations. It focuses on effecting a merger, consolidation, capital stock exchange, asset acquisition, stock purchase, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses or entities. It intends to identify business opportunities in the field of technology-driven business. The company was formerly known as Trajectory Alpha Acquisition Corp. and changed its name to Zalatoris Acquisition Corp. in June 2023. Zalatoris Acquisition Corp. was incorporated in 2021 and is based in New York, New York.
